OL,3,CLawyer dismisses claims of Lucy
OL,4,CLetby's innocence as 'purely
OL,5,Cspeculation'
OL,7,FThe lawyer representing families whose
OL,8,Fbabies were targeted by Lucy Letby has
OL,9,Fdismissed claims of her innocence as
OL,10,F"purely speculation."
OL,12,FTamlin Bolton, who represents the
OL,13,Ffamilies of six victims, described the
OL,14,Fclaims as "upsetting" for all of her
OL,15,Fclients.
OL,17,FShe spoke out following interviews
OL,18,Fgiven by Letby's new lawyer, barrister
OL,19,FMark McDonald, who says there is
OL,20,F"absolutely" a strong case for her
OL,21,Fbeing innocent.
