OL,7,FIt is believed Mr McDonald will make
OL,8,Fan application to the Criminal Cases
OL,9,FReview Commission (CCRC) for Letby's
OL,10,Fcase to be sent back to the Court of
OL,11,FAppeal.
OL,13,FLetby was convicted of the murders of
OL,14,Fseven babies and the attempted murders
OL,15,Fof seven others, with two attempts on
OL,16,Fone child, when she worked on the
OL,17,Fneonatal unit at the Countess of
OL,18,FChester Hospital between June 2015 and
OL,19,FJune 2016.
