OL,7,FSolicitor Tamlin Bolton represents the
OL,8,Ffamilies of six of Letby's victims.
OL,10,FLetby is serving 15 whole-life orders
OL,11,F` making her only the fourth woman in
OL,12,FUK history to be told she will never
OL,13,Fbe released from prison.
OL,15,FMs Bolton told ITV News:
OL,16,F"Fundamentally, Lucy Letby has been
OL,17,Ffound guilty of these crimes. She's
OL,18,Fexhausted her appeals process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
