OL,3,CLawyer dismisses claims of Lucy
OL,4,CLetby's innocence as 'purely
OL,5,Cspeculation'
OL,7,F"Those who have been privy to the full
OL,8,Fremit of evidence, including the
OL,9,Ffamilies, the jurors and the judges in
OL,10,Fthe Court of Appeal, have maintained
OL,11,Fher guilt. So anything outside of that
OL,12,Fis purely speculation.
OL,14,FSpeaking to BBC Breakfast on Monday 9
OL,15,FSeptember, the solicitor added: "I
OL,16,Fcan't stress enough how upsetting that
OL,17,Fhas been for all of the families that
OL,18,FI represent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
