OL,7,F"And they have thought about so many
OL,8,Fways in which they can try to address
OL,9,Fthat and deal with it and make sure
OL,10,Fthey put their voice across. But of
OL,11,Fcourse they're restricted by wanting
OL,12,Fto keep themselves confidential and
OL,13,Fprivate.
OL,15,F"So it's a really difficult challenge
OL,16,Ffor them to try and avoid social
OL,17,Fmedia, avoid the reporting about it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
