OL,8,Fthe Countess of Chester Hospital
OL,9,Ffollowing Letby's multiple convictions
OL,10,Fis due to begin on Tuesday 10
OL,11,FSeptember in Liverpool.
OL,13,FMs Bolton told ITV News the families
OL,14,Fshe represented wanted the inquiry to
OL,15,Fbe transparent, for there to be
OL,16,Faccountability for what happened and
OL,17,Ffor it to produce "robust"
OL,18,Frecommendations for change in
OL,19,Fmaternity care.
